race.comment: Happy to have MYSTIC REIGN (3) on top. Course and distance winner in stronger class here early in the year then struck a soft track at Caulfield in the spring and jockey reported didn't handle it. Given a break and presents on the back of two sharp jump-outs. Claim brings her right into this and the stable is flying. Goes close. WILTSHIRE SQUARE (12) also went to the paddock a winner and returns after a long spell. Fitter for three hit-outs, placed 2/2 fresh and nicely weighted with the claim. Expected to go well. MAUNA KEA MISS (9) ran on hard to score at Caulfield Heath latest and will be winding up late.  CAVALRY GIRL (10) is close to another win. Led and just missed at Caulfield last time. Course and distance winner with good speed and will give a sight again.
